data.description: Welcome to this Bi-Level home situated on an acre+ of land with an in-ground pool. Three bedrooms plus an office/4th bedroom on the lower level. Open kitchen dining room combo with sliders to the large deck which overlooks the pool. Large living room with brick wood burning fireplace and a large family room in the lower level. Beautiful landscaping, large shed, one car attached garage and plenty of storage. New roof in 2015, new pool pump in 2015. House has plenty to offer it's new homeowner.
